  "title": "分割一切并不够，还要 3D 重建一切，SAM 3D 来了",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651002688&idx=2&sn=b23a477296e32fb1397e239496fdca0b",
  "date": "2025-11-20 02:05:00",
